repository.name: rust-simple-event-driven-microservices
repository.description: "Simple Event-Driven Microservice Architecture in Rust" is an open-source project showcasing the simplicity and efficiency of building microservices in Rust. This minimalistic project demonstrates an e-commerce backend system, featuring just two microservices: Catalog and Order.
